1090
01:23:22,943 --> 01:23:24,363
And they don't get the attention that they deserve.

1091
01:23:24,383 --> 01:23:27,004
And then they have to come down to city hall and go back and go back to the back.

1092
01:23:27,264 --> 01:23:27,964
They're not going to vote.

1093
01:23:27,984 --> 01:23:29,105
They're just not going to do it.

1094
01:23:29,665 --> 01:23:32,986
