1194
01:29:01,349 --> 01:29:03,330
I don't know what the state does if we're not in compliance.

1195
01:29:03,410 --> 01:29:09,912
I just would prefer to be in compliance because I think it's important that we follow the rules that are given to us.

1196
01:29:10,812 --> 01:29:12,493
to uphold the integrity of the election.

1197
01:29:13,053 --> 01:29:19,615
I understand your frustration with the- I mean, you can't just throw a third of the people in the community off the voter rolls.

1198
01:29:19,635 --> 01:29:20,815
