1202
01:29:27,177 --> 01:29:27,397
Right?

1203
01:29:27,497 --> 01:29:28,537
I mean, that's what happens, right?

1204
01:29:28,677 --> 01:29:31,078
So it's hard enough to get people to want to participate.

1205
01:29:31,178 --> 01:29:32,578
And I just think that this is a failed policy.

1206
01:29:32,598 --> 01:29:34,099
It's not your policy.

1207
01:29:34,159 --> 01:29:35,179
It's just a failed policy.

1208
01:29:35,199 --> 01:29:36,979
You're saying it's to comply with the state law.

1209
01:29:36,999 --> 01:29:38,160
I think that doesn't make any sense.

1210
01:29:38,220 --> 01:29:38,660
It's crazy.

1211
01:29:39,340 --> 01:29:44,082
It's crazy if you fall off the, if you don't fill out your census form, but they not send you an excise tax bill, pretty sure they do.

1212
