1278
01:36:02,003 --> 01:36:09,088
I have heard this council reiterate many times that charter review should come from the people, and that is exactly what is happening.

1279
01:36:09,789 --> 01:36:14,032
We are all residents who volunteered for this task because we care about our city.

1280
01:36:14,913 --> 01:36:18,335
Our process prioritizes community engagement and input.

1281
01:36:18,856 --> 01:36:23,079
We will use the public feedback we collect to draft a proposal

1282
01:36:23,519 --> 01:36:29,325
that must make its way through several portals, including this council, before ever becoming official.

1283
01:36:29,965 --> 01:36:33,028
The final step is at the ballot box with the voters.

1284
01:36:33,629 --> 01:36:36,372
The voters, the people, will have the final say.

1285
01:36:37,652 --> 01:36:47,661
